        <p class="mv-card-text">To awaken and mobilize the global Church into Christ-centered unity, sacrificial love, and the full expression of the dominion mandate; fostering spiritual maturity, Kingdom authority, and all-round prosperity — spiritually, physically, and socially — until the Body of Christ attains the fullness of Christ.</p>
