        <h2 class="mv-card-heading">Advancing the Great Commission with Power</h2>
        <p class="mv-card-text">To advance the Great Commission as mandated in Mark 16:15–16 and Matthew 28:18–20 by proclaiming the Gospel of Jesus Christ with power, bringing holistic deliverance to individuals and communities, awakening global consciousness to the imminent return of our Lord Jesus Christ, and equipping believers to live in readiness, purity, and spiritual authority for His Second Coming.</p>
        <p class="mv-card-ref">Mark 16:15–16 · Matthew 28:18–20</p>
